description:
Tenkawa Maihime is the head of Kanagawa City. Nickname: Hime. She is the strongest princess who has reigned at the top of Kanagawa for a long time. She is idealistic and has a one-track mind, and her blunt behaviour makes her stand out. She is proud of her incredible physical strength, and she uses a huge gun to blast away her opponents in one hit.
Source: ANN
name: Tenkawa Maihime
